# SPEC-MINK-CROSSPLAT-001 M7 (PR #197): POSIX shell scripts and bats tests
# must remain LF on all platforms. Windows runners (used for WSL2 CI) default
# to core.autocrlf=true and would otherwise convert these files to CRLF,
# breaking dash/bash POSIX execution inside WSL2.
*.sh text eol=lf
*.bats text eol=lf
